title: Bonus Episode: The blessing and curse of the '90s Latin Pop Explosion
description: Our play cousins at NPR's It's Been a Minute podcast reexamine the so-called "Latin explosion" of the late '90s: What it was supposed to be for audiences across the U.S., and what it actually came to represent.
